      <h1 class='title'>Agency Workers Directive</h1>
    </div>
    <div class='commons-written-statements-sitting' id='content'>
      
      <cite class='section'>HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1720WS</cite>
      <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_1720ws' title='Col. 1720WS &mdash; HC Deb 16 September 2004 vol 424 c1720WS' name='column_1720ws' href='#column_1720ws' rel='bookmark'>1720WS</a>
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_409'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-henry-bellingham' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_409' title='Link to this speech by Mr Henry Bellingham' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-henry-bellingham" title="Mr Henry Bellingham">Mr. Bellingham</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">To ask the Secretary of State for Trade and Industry if she will make a statement on the Agency Workers Directive. [186338]</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_410'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0424P2_20040916_CWS2_410' title='Link to this speech by Mr Gerry Sutcliffe' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/mr-gerry-sutcliffe" title="Mr Gerry Sutcliffe">Mr. Sutcliffe</a></cite>
          <p class="first-para">Our position on the Agency Workers Directive remains that we support the principle of the directive but the text needs to be changed to meet the concerns of all member states. We are committed to using our best endeavours to reach an early settlement.</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
